--baidu-cloud-function-compute","name":"Baidu Cloud Function Compute","logo":"logos/3ad80fd36ad5c858388bfb96f1c0bdc3582714e48e974707cf2aa42d103c3439.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://cloud.baidu.com/product/cfc.html","description":"CFC (Cloud Function Compute) is a serverless solution provided by Baidu for enterprises and developers. It provides event-based, flexible, highly available, scalable and highly responsive cloud computing capabilities, and supports a variety of function triggers meeting a variety of scenarios.","member_subcategory":"Gold"},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--catalyst-by-zoho","name":"Catalyst by Zoho","logo":"logos/ef8b629197a1907438a6f7e1ff85e8beac8b8eaf0d5bbc209535e3db5a03afb0.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://catalyst.zoho.com/?utm_source=cncf","description":"Catalyst is a full-stack cloud development platform that enables you to build feature-rich applications. From building and testing to hosting and deploying, Catalyst streamlines your development cycle with a rich suite of Serverless components, Backend tools, DevOps, AI/ML capabilities and more."},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--cloudflare-workers","name":"Cloudflare Workers","logo":"logos/d1b80caf5889736274f8c7179e83f40e363fcfc0b8dc4ee4e5a3a8c50a2d4916.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://workers.cloudflare.com","description":"Cloudflare Workers provides a lightweight JavaScript execution environment that allows developers to augment existing applications or create entirely new ones without configuring or maintaining infrastructure."},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--google-cloud-run","name":"Google Cloud Run","logo":"logos/42a910e5d9f5a8685227f91623bf50c8c9259c556a41eb9a97157fd1e78b0cea.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://cloud.google.com/run/","description":"Cloud Run allows you to build and deploy scalable containerized apps written in any language (including Go, Python, Java, Node.js, .NET, and Ruby) on a fully managed serverless platform.","member_subcategory":"Platinum"},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--huawei-functionstage","name":"Huawei FunctionStage","logo":"logos/a9477dea89c660bec4c1ea550c9c0c79cdff1df66caff855569072e6b84cb55c.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://www.huaweicloud.com/intl/en-us","description":"FunctionStage is an event-driven function hosting and computing service, that compiles function code and configures running conditions without provisioning or managing servers, thus providing a scalable, maintenance-free, and reliable operation environment for functions. You only pay for what you use.","member_subcategory":"Platinum"},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--ibm-cloud-code-engine","name":"IBM Cloud Code Engine","logo":"logos/cafeb26076b4bef3909f16ef7a4e83dbc9735eef3cf8553106d32af8953de41a.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://cloud.ibm.com/login","description":"Host all your Cloud Native applications in one platform. You'll get all the benefits of serverless (no servers, auto-scaling) along with batch processing and only pay for what you use.","member_subcategory":"Platinum"},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--ibm-cloud-functions","name":"IBM Cloud Functions","logo":"logos/6454caee3f1fa01a6f5884ea43095daea4bd2df1c543bd339cb43810479f65b0.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://cloud.ibm.com/functions/","description":"Run your application code without servers, scale it automatically, and pay nothing when it's not in use.","member_subcategory":"Platinum"},{"category":"Serverless","id":"serverless--hosted-platform--koyeb","name":"Koyeb","logo":"logos/d14d20f65686508da4ef13e75d0951a14edf39603c71e5f0caf62a81aadb26a0.svg","subcategory":"Hosted Platform","website":"https://www.koyeb.com","description":"Koyeb is a developer-friendly serv